{"id":839,"date":"2021-04-14T02:50:17","date_gmt":"2021-04-14T02:50:17","guid":{"rendered":"http:\/\/programming.sdarobotics.org\/?page_id=839"},"modified":"2025-04-21T18:26:00","modified_gmt":"2025-04-21T18:26:00","slug":"installing-tools","status":"publish","type":"page","link":"http:\/\/gabybot.com\/installing-tools\/","title":{"rendered":"Installing Tools"},"content":{"rendered":"\n<p>This section will walk you through installing the tools necessary to use the tutorials on this site. Note that these instructions are for Windows installations only.  <\/p>\n\n\n\n<h4>Install Java jdk<\/h4>\n\n\n\n<p>The first step is to install the <strong>Java jdk 11<\/strong> which can be found here:<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p><a href=\"https:\/\/www.oracle.com\/java\/technologies\/javase-jdk11-downloads.html\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\">https:\/\/www.oracle.com\/java\/technologies\/javase-jdk11-downloads.html<\/a><\/p>\n\n\n\n<p>Download and install the <strong>Windows x64 Installer<\/strong>.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<h4>Install VS Code<\/h4>\n\n\n\n<p>If you have the version of <strong>Visual Studio Code<\/strong> that you use to program your FRC robot, you can use that to program the <strong>Minibots<\/strong>. Otherwise you will need to install <strong>Visual Studio Code for Java<\/strong> which can be found here:<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p><a rel=\"noreferrer noopener\" href=\"https:\/\/code.visualstudio.com\/docs\/languages\/java\" target=\"_blank\">https:\/\/code.visualstudio.com\/docs\/languages\/java<\/a><\/p>\n\n\n\n<h4>Robot Tools<\/h4>\n\n\n\n<p>The remaining robot tools can be found here: <a href=\"https:\/\/github.com\/Paradox2102\/RobotTools2025\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\">https:\/\/github.com\/Paradox2102\/RobotTools2025<\/a>.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-image\"><figure class=\"aligncenter size-full is-resized\"><img loading=\"lazy\" src=\"\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/07\/RobotTools2024.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"wp-image-2708\" width=\"530\" height=\"348\" srcset=\"http:\/\/gabybot.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/07\/RobotTools2024.jpg 837w, http:\/\/gabybot.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/07\/RobotTools2024-300x197.jpg 300w, http:\/\/gabybot.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/07\/RobotTools2024-150x98.jpg 150w, http:\/\/gabybot.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/07\/RobotTools2024-768x504.jpg 768w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 530px) 100vw, 530px\" \/><\/figure><\/div>\n\n\n\n<h4>Creating a Raspberry Pi Image<\/h4>\n\n\n\n<p>The <strong>Raspberry Pi<\/strong> image that you will need can be found <a rel=\"noreferrer noopener\" href=\"https:\/\/drive.google.com\/file\/d\/1oO3Tiu7Cjei9ZObWtFEr77biArVP-dUJ\/view?usp=sharing\" target=\"_blank\">here<\/a>. Flash this image onto an <strong>SD card<\/strong> that is at least <strong>8GB<\/strong>. Then boot your <strong>Raspberry Pi<\/strong> from the image.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p>The <strong>Raspberry Pi<\/strong> will show up as a <strong>WiFi <\/strong>hotspot named <strong>SwerveBot<\/strong>. Connect to that and then open a secure shell by typing:<\/p>\n\n\n\n<pre class=\"wp-block-code\"><code>ssh pi@10.21.2.2<\/code><\/pre>\n\n\n\n<p>The password is &#8216;<strong>raspberry<\/strong>&#8216; (without the quotes).<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p>The first thing you want to do is to <strong>expand <\/strong>the file system to match the size of the <strong>SD card<\/strong> that you chose. Do this by entering the following command on the <strong>Raspberry Pi<\/strong> command prompt:<\/p>\n\n\n\n<pre class=\"wp-block-code\"><code>raspi-config --expand-rootfs<\/code><\/pre>\n\n\n\n<p>Then reboot your <strong>Pi <\/strong>by typing:<\/p>\n\n\n\n<pre class=\"wp-block-code\"><code>sudo reboot now<\/code><\/pre>\n\n\n\n<p>You will then probably want to change the <strong>SSID <\/strong>of the hotspot so that all of your robots use a different <strong>ID<\/strong>. To do that, connect back to the <strong>PI <\/strong>with a secure shell and type:<\/p>\n\n\n\n<pre class=\"wp-block-code\"><code>sudo nmtui<\/code><\/pre>\n\n\n\n<p>This should open the following window:<\/p>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-image\"><figure class=\"aligncenter size-full is-resized\"><img loading=\"lazy\" src=\"\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/04\/nmtui2.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"wp-image-4260\" width=\"543\" height=\"297\" srcset=\"http:\/\/gabybot.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/04\/nmtui2.jpg 763w, http:\/\/gabybot.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/04\/nmtui2-300x164.jpg 300w, http:\/\/gabybot.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/04\/nmtui2-150x82.jpg 150w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 543px) 100vw, 543px\" \/><\/figure><\/div>\n\n\n\n<p>Press <strong>Enter <\/strong>and you should get the following window:<\/p>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-image\"><figure class=\"aligncenter size-full is-resized\"><img loading=\"lazy\" src=\"\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/04\/nmtui3.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"wp-image-4262\" width=\"540\" height=\"295\" srcset=\"http:\/\/gabybot.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/04\/nmtui3.jpg 763w, http:\/\/gabybot.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/04\/nmtui3-300x164.jpg 300w, http:\/\/gabybot.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/04\/nmtui3-150x82.jpg 150w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 540px) 100vw, 540px\" \/><\/figure><\/div>\n\n\n\n<p>Cursor down to the <strong>SwerveBot <\/strong>entry and press <strong>Enter<\/strong>. You should then get the following:<\/p>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-image\"><figure class=\"aligncenter size-full is-resized\"><img loading=\"lazy\" src=\"\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/04\/nmtui4.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"wp-image-4265\" width=\"548\" height=\"299\" srcset=\"http:\/\/gabybot.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/04\/nmtui4.jpg 763w, http:\/\/gabybot.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/04\/nmtui4-300x164.jpg 300w, http:\/\/gabybot.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/04\/nmtui4-150x82.jpg 150w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 548px) 100vw, 548px\" \/><\/figure><\/div>\n\n\n\n<p>Cursor down to the <strong>SSID <\/strong>field and change the <strong>SSID <\/strong>to whatever you want:<\/p>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-image\"><figure class=\"aligncenter size-full is-resized\"><img loading=\"lazy\" src=\"\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/04\/nmtui5.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"wp-image-4266\" width=\"562\" height=\"307\" srcset=\"http:\/\/gabybot.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/04\/nmtui5.jpg 763w, http:\/\/gabybot.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/04\/nmtui5-300x164.jpg 300w, http:\/\/gabybot.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/04\/nmtui5-150x82.jpg 150w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 562px) 100vw, 562px\" \/><\/figure><\/div>\n\n\n\n<p>Then cursor all the way to the bottom, choose the <strong>OK <\/strong>option and press <strong>Enter<\/strong>.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-image\"><figure class=\"aligncenter size-full is-resized\"><img loading=\"lazy\" src=\"\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/04\/nmtui6.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"wp-image-4267\" width=\"568\" height=\"310\" srcset=\"http:\/\/gabybot.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/04\/nmtui6.jpg 763w, http:\/\/gabybot.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/04\/nmtui6-300x164.jpg 300w, http:\/\/gabybot.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/04\/nmtui6-150x82.jpg 150w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 568px) 100vw, 568px\" \/><\/figure><\/div>\n\n\n\n<p>Then tab over to the <strong>Back <\/strong>button and press <strong>Enter<\/strong><\/p>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-image\"><figure class=\"aligncenter size-full is-resized\"><img loading=\"lazy\" src=\"\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/04\/nmtui7.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"wp-image-4268\" width=\"571\" height=\"312\" srcset=\"http:\/\/gabybot.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/04\/nmtui7.jpg 763w, http:\/\/gabybot.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/04\/nmtui7-300x164.jpg 300w, http:\/\/gabybot.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/04\/nmtui7-150x82.jpg 150w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 571px) 100vw, 571px\" \/><\/figure><\/div>\n\n\n\n<p>Finally cursor down to the <strong>Quit <\/strong>option and press <strong>Enter<\/strong>.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-image\"><figure class=\"aligncenter size-full is-resized\"><img loading=\"lazy\" src=\"\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/04\/nmtui8.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"wp-image-4269\" width=\"587\" height=\"321\" srcset=\"http:\/\/gabybot.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/04\/nmtui8.jpg 763w, http:\/\/gabybot.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/04\/nmtui8-300x164.jpg 300w, http:\/\/gabybot.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/04\/nmtui8-150x82.jpg 150w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 587px) 100vw, 587px\" \/><\/figure><\/div>\n\n\n\n<p>Then reboot your <strong>Pi <\/strong>and it should come as the newly named <strong>hotspot<\/strong>.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p>You are now ready to follow the instructions in the <strong><a href=\"\/robot-java\/\" data-type=\"page\" data-id=\"23\">Minibot<\/a> <\/strong>and\/or <a href=\"\/swervebot\/\" data-type=\"page\" data-id=\"2721\"><strong>SwerveBot <\/strong><\/a>tutorials to create and run your own robot programs.<\/p>\n","protected":false},"excerpt":{"rendered":"<p>This section will walk you through installing the tools necessary to use the tutorials on this site. Note that these instructions are for Windows installations only. Install Java jdk The first step is to install the Java jdk 11 which can be found here: https:\/\/www.oracle.com\/java\/technologies\/javase-jdk11-downloads.html Download and install the Windows x64 Installer. Install VS Code&hellip;&nbsp;<a href=\"http:\/\/gabybot.com\/installing-tools\/\" class=\"\" rel=\"bookmark\">Read More &raquo;<span class=\"screen-reader-text\">Installing Tools<\/span><\/a><\/p>\n","protected":false},"author":2,"featured_media":0,"parent":0,"menu_order":0,"comment_status":"closed","ping_status":"open","template":"","meta":{"neve_meta_sidebar":"","neve_meta_container":"","neve_meta_enable_content_width":"","neve_meta_content_width":0,"neve_meta_title_alignment":"","neve_meta_author_avatar":"","neve_post_elements_order":"","neve_meta_disable_header":"","neve_meta_disable_footer":"","neve_meta_disable_title":""},"_links":{"self":[{"href":"http:\/\/gabybot.com\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/pages\/839"}],"collection":[{"href":"http:\/\/gab